          "tz": 330
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Noopur Maheshwari",
          "email": "noopur.maheshwari@seagate.com",
          "date": "2016-01-12 20:10:36.000000000",
          "tz": 330
        },
        "subject": "LU-7656 tests: tar a temporary folder",
        "message": "LU-7656 tests: tar a temporary folder\n\ntar on /etc folder leads to various \"No such\nfile or directory\" failures for different files\nin the /etc folder.\n\nSince the main purpose of this test is to check\nmdt recovery while tar runs in a loop, instead\nof performing a tar on the /etc folder, the fix\nis to create a temporary folder with n files in\nit and perform a tar on this temporary folder.\nAfter the tar process is killed, remove this\ntemporary folder.\n\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-2925\nSigned-off-by: Noopur Maheshwari <noopur.maheshwari@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I62c4f9855c028094675bde222b630e6c847b95ac\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
